[No. 6,057.] KELLOGG v. MAYER, Administrator, etc. Dismissal of Appeal—Tbakscript. The facts are as stated in the argument of respondent’s counsel. No brief on file for Appellant.

Gunnison & Booth, for Respondent.

The transcript does not comply with the rules of this Court. There is no index, and the lines are not folioed.

Department No. 1:

On motion, ordered that appeal be dismissed.
